      "heading": null,
      "description": "Split the pitta in half so you have two thin layers of bread. Cut into whatever shape you fancy, I’ve gone for triangles."
    },
    {
      "heading": null,
      "description": "In a mixing bowl, combine your garlic powder, onion powder, your remaining oregano, salt and pepper. Add the pitta pieces to the bowl and stir to coat."
    },
